### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Airport lookup — known city
POST http://localhost:3000/api/airports
Content-Type: application/json

{ "query": "Tokyo" }

### Airport lookup — unknown city (expect 404)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/airports
Content-Type: application/json

{ "query": "Fakecity" }

### Flight search
POST http://localhost:3000/api/flights
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originQuery": "New York City",
  "destinationQuery": "Tokyo",
  "departureDate": "2026-06-15",
  "adults": 1
}

### Flight search — missing field (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/flights
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originQuery": "Paris"
}
